# Presentation outputs

Rendered presentation files land here.

Layout:
- `<slug>.pptx` — single PPTX
- `<slug>/index.html` + `assets/` — HTML deck root
- `v1/...`, `v2/...` — variant outputs when `variants>1`
- `<slug>.pdf` — optional PDF export
- `<slug>-handout.pdf` — optional handout (1-up / 2-up / 6-up layouts)

`/bq-presentation` writes here only when the user explicitly requests implementation. Until then, only planning artifacts (BRIEF, OUTLINE, SLIDE_PLAN, DESIGN_BRIEF, MOTION_PLAN, SPEAKER_NOTES, REFERENCES) exist.

The tool used for rendering is decided per `.bequite/principles/TOOL_NEUTRALITY.md` (no default library installed).
